---
// components/MethodologyResult.astro
---

<section
    class="relative w-full bg-black py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden"
>
    <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center"
    >
        <!-- Content Card -->
        <div
            class="w-full lg:w-1/2 p-10 md:p-14 rounded-[3rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-3xl"
        >
            <h2
                class="text-[#aba070] font-bold tracking-widest text-sm mb-4 uppercase italic"
            >
                EL OBJETIVO
            </h2>
            <h3
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tighter uppercase"
            >
                EL RESULTADO FINAL
            </h3>

            <div
                class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed"
            >
                <p>
                    El resultado del método <span class="text-white font-bold"
                        >De Cero a Fitness®</span
                    > es simple de explicar y potente de vivir:
                </p>

                <div
                    class="p-8 bg-[#aba070]/10 rounded-3xl border border-[#aba070]/20"
                >
                    <p
                        class="text-white font-medium italic text-xl leading-relaxed"
                    >
                        "Pasas de no saber por dónde empezar a ser una persona
                        que entrena con seguridad, come con criterio y domina su
                        propio progreso."
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[#aba070]/30">
                        <p
                            class="text-[#aba070] font-black text-sm tracking-widest uppercase"
                        >
                            UNA VIDA FITNESS QUE ES TUYA PARA SIEMPRE.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Image Card -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative group">
            <div
                class="absolute -inset-4 bg-orange-500/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full opacity-50"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="relative aspect-[4/5] rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-3xl transform transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-[1.02]"
            >
                <img
                    src="/images/7.webp"
                    alt="Resultados del método De Cero a Fitness"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover brightness-90 group-hover:brightness-100 transition-all duration-700"
                    loading="lazy"
                />
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent"
                >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style></style>
